[But I always believed that]

106
00:06:48,100 --> 00:06:49,500
[as long as I worked hard]

107
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:51,060
[to be outstanding,]

108
00:06:51,740 --> 00:06:53,640
[I could still conquer the world]

109
00:06:54,140 --> 00:06:55,320
[with my talent.]

110
00:07:05,020 --> 00:07:06,640
I have drawn another one

111
