woman to win a Nobel Prize.

118
00:07:22,660 --> 00:07:24,180
Her accomplishments have surpassed

119
00:07:24,180 --> 00:07:25,490
all men from her era.

120
00:07:28,260 --> 00:07:29,320
In my impression,

121
00:07:30,020 --> 00:07:31,810
she represents female power.

122
00:07:33,980 --> 00:07:35,080
[And I can see]

123
00:07:36,580 --> 00:07:38,600
[the same power from your works.]

124
00:07:41,980 --> 00:07:44,520
[It stems from your talent and ambition,]

125
00:07:47,180 --> 00:07:48,780
[not from your appearance.]

126
00:07:52,500 --> 00:07:53,630
[I believe one day,]

127
00:07:54,700 --> 00:07:55,840
[your old self]

128
00:07:57,540 --> 00:07:58,610
[will become]

129
00:07:58,610 --> 00:08:00,340
[a world-renowned designer.]

130
00:08:12,940 --> 00:08:13,710
Thank you.

131
00:08:21,780 --> 00:08:23,040
The third fabrication

132
00:08:24,050 --> 00:08:25,920
is The Death of Marat itself.

133
00:08:26,860 --> 00:08:28,320
The Death of Marat itself?

134
00:08:28,500 --> 00:08:29,820
It's unexpected, isn't it?

135
00:08:29,820 --> 00:08:30,880
The artist has been

136
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:33,330
deceiving us from the get-go.

137
00:08:34,740 --> 00:08:35,720
The key secret

138
00:08:36,620 --> 00:08:37,740
lies on the note

139
00:08:37,740 --> 00:08:38,669
in Marat's hand.

140
00:08:39,419 --> 00:08:40,559
On the note,

141
00:08:41,490 --> 00:08:42,330
it says Corday

142
00:08:42,330 --> 00:08:43,610
was asking Marat for help.

143
00:08:43,419 --> 00:08:46,240
[Of 13 July 1793. Marie Anne Charlotte Corday to Citizen Marat.]

144
00:08:44,580 --> 00:08:46,130
Marat was going to fund her.

145
00:08:46,250 --> 00:08:49,170
[Given that I am unhappy, I am entitled to your benevolence.]

146
00:08:46,700 --> 00:08:48,360
But that's not what happened.

147
00:08:49,180 --> 00:08:50,580
Before Marat was killed,

148
00:08:51,060 --> 00:08:52,760
his last words to the world

149
00:08:53,540 --> 00:08:55,540
turned out to be a list of offenders.

150
00:08:56,740 --> 00:08:57,650
That's the truth

151
00:08:57,650 --> 00:08:59,210
hidden under the note.

152
00:08:59,540 --> 00:09:00,800
The names in the list

153
00:09:00,980 --> 00:09:01,980
were dissidents whom

154
00:09:01,980 --> 00:09:03,650
Marat wanted to execute.

155
00:09:04,140 --> 00:09:05,960
Corday was brave enough to

156
00:09:06,180 --> 00:09:07,060
meet Marat alone

157
00:09:07,060 --> 00:09:08,520
and stop him from killing.

158
00:09:08,780 --> 00:09:10,570
Corday once testified that

159
00:09:11,330 --> 00:09:12,410
she killed one man

160
00:09:13,900 --> 00:09:15,640
to save 100,000.

161
00:09:18,460 --> 00:09:19,640
From ancient murals

162
00:09:20,140 --> 00:09:22,070
to Rembrandt's "The Night Watch",

163
00:09:22,420 --> 00:09:24,040
artists have always been

164
00:09:24,340 --> 00:09:26,340
responsible for preserving history

165
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:28,270
and restoring important moments.

166
00:09:29,380 --> 00:09:30,200
However,

167
00:09:30,380 --> 00:09:31,480
one small alteration

168
00:09:31,480 --> 00:09:32,920
to the painting

169
00:09:33,170 --> 00:09:35,040
has turned Marat from a killer

170
00:09:35,490 --> 00:09:36,960
into a philanthropist,

171
00:09:37,580 --> 00:09:38,840
and stigmatised

172
00:09:39,660 --> 00:09:40,770
a heroine.

173
00:09:41,340 --> 00:09:43,360
The history and scenes of paintings

174
00:09:43,660 --> 00:09:45,320
are often mixed with falsity.

175
00:09:45,980 --> 00:09:46,740
We may have to

176
00:09:46,740 --> 00:09:48,670
spend a lifetime to identify them.

177
00:09:50,860 --> 00:09:52,520
You've handled the case well.

178
00:09:52,740 --> 00:09:53,290
I heard

179
00:09:53,290 --> 00:09:54,520
you two made a bet.

180
00:09:55,060 --> 00:09:55,760
Du Cheng.

181
00:09:56,020 --> 00:09:57,320
You bet, you pay.

182
00:09:58,660 --> 00:09:59,460
Do you admit defeat?

183
00:09:59,460 --> 00:09:59,890
Yes.

184
