Try to spend time with veteran comrades

194
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:21,140
and learn new things.

195
00:10:22,180 --> 00:10:23,520
Yes, I will.

196
00:10:24,100 --> 00:10:25,230
Bureau Chief Zhang.

197
00:10:25,490 --> 00:10:27,210
Shen Yi is a newcomer.

